snippet.title: Liar! Scheming Socialites - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
It's the newest installment in the romance + mystery app series, "Liar: Uncover the Truth!"
Coming in July!

You're a student at a top private university, having the time of your life... when your family suddenly decides to push you into an arranged marriage?!
To change your parents' minds, you need a boyfriend they'll approve of...

You only have until graduation...
Your path to freedom is blocked by a bunch of liars?!

Your fate rests on finding the perfect boyfriend...


Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/LiarUncoverTheTruth

▼Liar! Uncover the Truth @ the App Store & Google Play Store
https://app.adjust.com/9pazoi
